txt.en: Wanted: Hardened carapaces from the spiders and insects surrounding Thorenhad. All items should be delivered to a collection box.
You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
You have not recovered enough hardened carapaces for the Elves at Thorenhad.
Elves of Rivendell Task: Hardened Carapaces
The Elves at Thorenhad desire a delivery of hardened carapaces to be made to them.
Deliver the hardened carapaces to the collection box at Thorenhad in the Trollshaws

You have accepted a task to collect hardened carapaces from the spiders and insects in the areas surrounding Thorenhad. The items are to be delivered to a collection box. There is a collection box at Thorenhad in the Trollshaws.
Wanted: Hardened carapaces from the spiders and insects surrounding Thorenhad.
